column2: "I'm used to having to wait for people, but this is really too long."
"He said that he was definitely coming back, so I should try to accept that...."
"I wonder what he'll say when he sees me. He'll probably get mad."
"\"Why are you doing a class that doesn't fit you?\", like he's one to talk, though."
"Since we'll always be together, I thought it would be good for us to spend some time to ourselves."
"But still, where is he? What is he doing? And why won't he come back?"
"D-Did you hear what I said just now?"
"R-right, of course, you didn't hear anything!"
"All right, time to get back to doing ARKS, uh stuff! Yeah, that's it!"
"Oh, and I was wondering if you could help me investigate next time? You will right?\u3000Of course you will."
"... Don't tell Echo that I'm okay."
